abstract: MLB Roundup; Chicago Cubs beat Los Angeles Dodgers, 4-2; other baseball news noted.
lead_paragraph: Bryant homered twice for his first career multihomer game, and Chicago received terrific contributions from five relievers to beat the Los Angeles Dodgers.

headline.main: Cubs Solve Clayton Kershaw, as Kris Bryant Achieves a First
headline.print_headline: Cubs Solve Kershaw, as Bryant Achieves a First
